:52","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_931d8aee.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"爱范儿","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":22,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_91107228","title":"2026-02-02 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-02-02-HackerNews/","date":"2026-02-02 08:45:56","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_91107228.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":92,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_7c758f8","title":"“人人皆可开发”：v0 如何将 Git 工作流引入氛围编程 | Guillermo Rauch (Vercel CEO)","link":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yb9IyTOh0xg","date":"2026-02-04 13:01:11","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_7c758f8.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"How I AI","resourceType":"VIDEO","readTime":24,"score":93},{"id":"RAW_1ab141d","title":"Codex 应用介绍","link":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HFM3se4lNiw","date":"2026-02-02 22:16:58","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_1ab141d.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"OpenAI","resourceType":"VIDEO","readTime":8,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_1e21bd3","title":"EP76《人生设计课》：你的人生不需要「最优解」","link":"https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/episode/69844eacc78b823892cc5494","date":"2026-02-05 16:00:00","oneSentenceSummary":"基于斯坦福设计思维，系统拆解人生设计的十步法，帮助听众建立个人操作系统，应对职业迷茫与生活困境。","summary":"本期播客深入探讨了由斯坦福大学教授比尔·博内特和戴夫·埃文斯开创的“人生设计”方法论。内容围绕如何利用设计思维（Design Thinking）解决职场与人生的迷茫，强调人生并不存在单一的“最优解”，而是需要不断迭代和原型测试。节目详细解析了十个实践步骤，包括：1. 校准问题，识别并接受不可改变的“重力问题”；2. 通过“健康、工作、娱乐、爱”四驱仪表盘进行现状评估；3. 定义个人“北极星”（工作观与人生观）；4. 记录“美好时光日志”以管理心流与能耗；5. 利用思维导图发散职业可能性；6. 构建多元的人生计划（BCDE 计划）；7. 进行原型设计与访谈以低成本试错；8. 优化求职策略；9. 建立快速取舍的决策机制；10. 重构失败观。通过这些工具，听众可以学会如何从“能量管理”而非简单的“时间管理”出发，构建一个自洽且具备韧性的生活系统。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_1e21bd3.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"纵横四海","resourceType":"PODCAST","readTime":6,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_7129a87","ti